data.title: Kevin Garnett, Basketball Player
data.meta_description: Kevin Garnett stats and bio. Stats averages season by season. Quick access to game by game stats.
data.text:
Kevin Garnett - Points

Kevin Garnett scores a career high 47 points (2005)

On January 04, 2005, Kevin Garnett set his career high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 47 points in Minnesota's home loss against Phoenix, 115-122. He also had 17 rebounds, 4 assists, 2 steals. He shot 19/27 from two, 0/1 from three, shooting at 67.9% from the field. He also shot 9/11 from the free-throw line.

Kevin Garnett - Rebounds

Kevin Garnett grabs a career high 25 rebounds (2003)

On December 05, 2003, Kevin Garnett tied his career high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 25 rebounds in Minnesota's road win against Sacramento, 109-112. He also had 33 points, 6 assists, 1 steal and 3 blocks.

Kevin Garnett - Assists

Kevin Garnett gives a career high 12 assists (2003)

On March 09, 2003, Kevin Garnett tied his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 12 assists in Minnesota's road win against Phoenix, 98-105. He also had 29 points, 14 rebounds, 1 steal and 2 blocks.

Kevin Garnett - Steals

Kevin Garnett has a career high 7 steals (2007)

On January 27, 2007, Kevin Garnett tied his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 7 steals in Minnesota's road win against LA Clippers, 87-101. He also had 32 points, 9 rebounds and 3 assists.

Kevin Garnett - Blocks

Kevin Garnett blocks a career high 8 shots (1997)

On January 03, 1997, Kevin Garnett tied his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 8 blocks in Minnesota's road win against Boston, 84-94. He also had 16 points, 6 rebounds and 3 assists.

Kevin Garnett - Efficiency

Kevin Garnett records a career high 59 efficiency rating (2003)

On February 16, 2003, Kevin Garnett set his career high in efficiency in a NBA game. That day he accomplished 59 efficiency in Minnesota's home win against Golden State, 109-102. He also had 37 points, 22 rebounds and 6 assists.
